private ThreeWhiteSoldiers _threewhitesoldiers;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_threewhitesoldiers = ThreeWhiteSoldiers(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_threewhitesoldiers.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "ThreeWhiteSoldiers Period", _threewhitesoldiers.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "ThreeWhiteSoldiers Current", _threewhitesoldiers.Current);
